    <x-sections.card-image-with-text
        image="/images/custom-shirts/top5pct-banner-custom-apparel-custom-shirts-custom-hoodies-custom-caps.jpg"
        alt="Custom branded tote bags and drawstring bags for businesses and events in Joliet Illinois"
        title="Walking Billboards for Your Brand"
    >
        <p class="mb-4">Custom branded bags are one of the highest-visibility promotional products available because every bag that carries your logo is a moving advertisement that your customers take with them wherever they go. Tote bags and drawstring bags get used repeatedly at the grocery store, the gym, the beach, school, and everywhere in between, putting your brand in front of new eyes every single time, and for a complete brand kit that pairs with tote bags our <a href="/stickers/custom-shaped-stickers-decals" class="link-notification">custom stickers</a> make a great addition to any event swag package. Businesses, schools, churches, gyms, and organizations throughout Joliet, Will and DuPage County use custom bags to build brand recognition throughout the community in a practical and genuinely useful way, and many of our clients match their tote bags with <a href="/custom-apparel/group-wear/spirit-wear-shirts" class="link-notification">spirit wear</a> for a fully coordinated team and merchandise program.</p>
        <p class="mb-4">We produce custom tote bags and drawstring bags with full-color printing using dye sublimation and screen printing methods depending on the bag material and your design. Polyester drawstring bags accept dye sublimation for vibrant all-over designs, while cotton canvas tote bags are typically screen-printed for a clean, classic look. Both options are durable, reusable, and available in a range of sizes and colors to match your brand palette, and for a complete branded gift set our <a href="/promotional-items/mugs" class="link-notification">custom mugs</a> pair naturally with tote bags so your client or team member gets a full branded set in one package.</p>
        <p class="mb-4">We also offer <a href="/custom-apparel/printing-options/screen-printing" class="link-notification">screen printing</a> on canvas tote bags for bold, one or two color designs at bulk pricing, a great option when you need a large quantity with a simple, clean logo. Bundle tote bags with <a href="/promotional-items/mugs" class="link-notification">mugs</a> and koozies for a complete branded gift set where every item carries the same logo. Pair tote bags with <a href="/custom-apparel/group-wear/corporate-wear-shirts" class="link-notification">corporate wear</a> to create a unified brand identity across your team and your merchandise at every public event.</p>
        <p>Custom bags from <a href="/" class="link-notification">Top 5 Percent</a> are popular for event swag bags, trade show giveaways, school spirit merchandise, retail packaging, and corporate gift sets. No minimums and fast turnaround on all orders. Call us at <a href="tel:+18153498600" class="link-notification">(815) 349-8600</a> or visit 121 Springfield Avenue in Joliet to discuss your custom bag project today.</p>
    </x-sections.card-image-with-text>

    <x-sections.card-image-with-text
        image="/images/custom-shirts/top5pct-custom-reflective-shirts-hoodies-caps-joliet.jpg"
        alt="Custom canvas tote bags and polyester drawstring bags for businesses and events in Joliet Illinois"
        title="Canvas Totes and Polyester Drawstring Bags"
        imagePosition="right"
    >
        <p class="mb-4">Canvas tote bags are the classic choice for businesses that want a premium feel with an eco-conscious message. Natural cotton canvas has a quality look and feel that communicates sustainability and care for the environment, and the surface takes screen printing beautifully for a clean, crisp logo placement, and for businesses that want their crew in matching attire alongside their branded bags our <a href="/custom-apparel/group-wear/spirit-wear-shirts" class="link-notification">spirit wear</a> shop produces coordinating shirts and hoodies in the same order. Canvas totes are popular for boutique retail shops, organic food businesses, wellness brands, and any organization that wants their branded bag to communicate quality and environmental values, and many of our clients add <a href="/promotional-items/can-koozies" class="link-notification">can koozies</a> to their tote order for a complete branded event kit that covers bags, drinkware, and apparel in one appointment.</p>
        <p class="mb-4">Polyester drawstring bags offer a more athletic, active aesthetic and accept dye sublimation printing for vibrant all-over designs that cover the entire bag surface. They are lightweight, packable, and practical for school use, gym use, event swag bags, and anywhere that a versatile everyday bag is needed. Many schools and sports organizations throughout Joliet, Will and DuPage County use branded drawstring bags for spirit merchandise, team gear bags, and student incentive programs, and many event organizers add <a href="/promotional-items/can-koozies" class="link-notification">can koozies</a> to drawstring bag orders for a complete branded team kit.</p>
        <p>We also produce non-woven polypropylene bags, which are an economical option for large-quantity event giveaways and trade show distributions where you need a large number of branded bags at a lower per-unit cost. Contact us to discuss which bag type and printing method makes the most sense for your specific application and budget. Call us at <a href="tel:+18153498600" class="link-notification">(815) 349-8600</a> to get started.</p>
    </x-sections.card-image-with-text>

