        <x-slot name="intro">
            <p class="mb-4">Promotional products research consistently shows that branded bags generate more impressions per item than nearly any other category of promotional product. This is because a bag is used in public settings, carried through stores, taken to schools, brought to the gym, used at events, where it is seen by many people at once rather than just the person who owns it. A branded tote bag carried through a busy grocery store or farmers market is a mobile advertisement viewed by dozens of people every single time it is used, and for a complete branded event kit our <a href="/promotional-items/mugs" class="link-notification">custom mugs</a> pair naturally with tote bags in a gift set that covers bags, drinkware, and branded keepsakes.</p>
            <h3 class="text-h3 font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Impressions That Extend Far Beyond the Recipient</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">When you give someone a branded tote bag, you are not just creating a single brand impression with that one person. You are creating a walking advertisement that generates new brand impressions every time it leaves their house. A branded bag used once a week generates more than fifty public brand exposures per year, without any additional investment on your part. For local businesses in Joliet, Will and DuPage County that depend on community recognition, this kind of persistent, organic brand exposure in local public spaces is extraordinarily valuable.</p>
        </x-slot>
        <x-slot name="mid">
            <h3 class="text-h3 font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">A Useful Gift That Gets Kept and Used</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">Unlike many promotional items that get glanced at and set aside, a quality branded bag is actively useful and gets kept. Most people have a collection of canvas totes or drawstring bags that they reach for regularly for specific purposes, a dedicated grocery bag, a gym bag, a library bag, an errand bag. If your branded bag earns a spot in that regular rotation, it becomes part of the recipient's daily routine and generates brand impressions continuously without any further investment, and for a branded kit that pairs with tote bags our <a href="/promotional-items/mugs" class="link-notification">custom mugs</a> complement the bag with a daily touchpoint that keeps the logo visible from the grocery store to the office. For teams that want matching gear bags alongside their tote orders our <a href="/custom-apparel/group-wear/spirit-wear-shirts" class="link-notification">spirit wear</a> shop coordinates branded apparel with every bag order.</p>
            <h3 class="text-h3 font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Popular for Trade Shows and Event Swag</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">Event organizers and trade show exhibitors throughout the Chicagoland area rely on branded bags as the primary swag bag for distributing other materials, samples, and giveaways at their events. When an attendee carries your branded bag through an event venue to collect materials from other exhibitors, your logo is displayed prominently to every other exhibitor and attendee they pass. Few other giveaways provide this kind of in-event visibility for the distributing organization, and for a complete event swag experience our <a href="/promotional-items/can-koozies" class="link-notification">can koozies</a> make a great addition to any branded swag bag for a full branded drinkware set.</p>
        </x-slot>
        <x-slot name="lower">
            <h3 class="text-h3 font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Environmental Message Alignment</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">Reusable branded bags send a positive environmental message that resonates strongly with today's consumers. By providing a quality reusable bag, you are helping your customers reduce single-use plastic bag consumption while keeping your brand visible every time they use it as an alternative, and for a sustainably minded brand kit that pairs with eco-friendly tote bags our <a href="/promotional-items/mugs" class="link-notification">branded mugs</a> also position your company as one that values quality and practicality over disposable marketing. This environmental alignment creates a positive brand association that is difficult to achieve through traditional advertising, and for clients who want to extend that eco-conscious brand message to their team our <a href="/custom-apparel" class="link-notification">custom apparel</a> shop produces branded shirts and workwear that carries the same values from the bag to the uniform.</p>
        </x-slot>
        <x-slot name="footer">
            <p class="mb-4">We are a veteran owned print shop at 121 Springfield Avenue in Joliet, Illinois. We produce custom branded bags in a range of materials and printing methods for businesses, events, and organizations throughout Will and DuPage County and the Chicagoland area, and our full <a href="/promotional-items" class="link-notification">promotional items shop</a> includes mugs, can koozies, mouse pads, drink coasters, and towels so your entire event or gift kit comes from one team. For clients who want branded apparel alongside their bag order our <a href="/custom-apparel" class="link-notification">custom apparel</a> shop produces shirts and hoodies that coordinate with any tote bag design.</p>
            <p>Call us at <a href="tel:+18153498600" class="link-notification">(815) 349-8600</a> to discuss your custom tote or drawstring bag order, no minimums, multiple material options, and fast turnaround, and ask about bundling with our <a href="/promotional-items/can-koozies" class="link-notification">custom can koozies</a> for a complete branded event kit.</p>
        </x-slot>
